aims.text: When the occupant says 'on' or 'off', the light switches accordingly.
The light turns on automatically when the room is too dark.

rulesets.text: If the ambient light sensor detects a low reading, turn on the smart bulb.
If the ambient light sensor detects a high reading, turn on the smart bulb.
If the voice assistant receives a command to turn the light on or off, switch the smart bulb accordingly.
If the voice assistant receives a command to control the light sensor, enable or disable the sensor accordingly.
